span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:screenshot</strong> - Tira uma foto do ecrã (tela) para depois guardá-la;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:setspeed x&nbsp;</strong>- X é um numero de 0 a 20, altera a velocidade dos rollers;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:pickall</strong> - Recolhe todos mobis do dono do quarto;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:ejectall</strong> - Recolhe todos mobis de todos usuários do quarto;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:follow x</strong> - X é o nick do usuário, digite-o para seguí-lo;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:home</strong> - Vai para seu cafofo (quarto inicial);</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:diagonal&nbsp;</strong>- Ativa/desativa os Habbletianos em andar em diagonal;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:shake</strong> - Movimenta o quarto somente para você;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>:jump</strong> - Faz seu avatar dar um mini-salto;</span></span></s